    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried calling my doctor's office but they're closed for the weekend and i don't want to miss any doses of my cholesterol meds. i looked it up online and i can't tell if it's a major thing or just a minor thing. could you just tell me if there's a specific way i should space them out so i'm safe? like can i just take them at different times of the day?",
