    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, 2-3 hours apart? i read somewhere that certain antibiotics can actually make the statin levels spike in your blood which is dangerous. if i just take them a few hours apart, will that actually stop the interaction or is it still going to be a problem? i'm worried about the muscle thing you mentioned.",
